# Ideas Parking Lot

> A holding space for ideas that aren't ready for action yet. Park them here, let them marinate, and promote the good ones when the time is right.

---

## Idea Lifecycle

```
💡 Captured → 🔍 Evaluated → ⬆️ Promoted | 🗑️ Discarded
```

| Status | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| 💡 **New** | Just captured, not yet evaluated |
| 🔍 **Evaluating** | Actively thinking about feasibility |
| ⏸️ **On Hold** | Good idea, but not the right time |
| ⬆️ **Promoted** | Moved to Projects or Business/Ideas |
| 🗑️ **Discarded** | Decided against pursuing |

---

